des:
Wizcart uses technology that brings the personalization and convenience of eCommerce shopping to physical stores. Wizcart.shop was conceived in 2016 by a bunch of creative thinkers who got together to make this retail dream a reality.
 Self-scanning and self-service checkout are taking the shopping world by storm. However, grocery remains a challenge as it is the most complex and technically challenging retail format to provide mobile self-scanning for. 

Refer site as http://wizcart.shop
